data.description: LARGE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Fully remodeled ranch home just minutes from Gainesville and I985! Now's your chance to own a 4-sided brick home with low maintenance featuring all major appliances less than two years old! This 3 bed 2 bath home features a large, flat back yard,  garage, and a fully renovated interior. With the the roof, HVAC systems, porch, fresh paint (interior and exterior), granite countertops, kitchen appliances, flooring, etc. etc. etc. all replaced within the last 2 years, you'll be impressed with this move-in ready home. Schedule your appointment today and come see for yourself!
